---
import CalButton from '../../CalButton.astro'
---

<section class='relative overflow-hidden py-24 md:py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-surface to-base'>
  <!-- Ambient light gradients -->
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="absolute -top-20 -right-10 h-[400px] w-[500px] rounded-full bg-cream/15 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 -left-20 h-[320px] w-[400px] rounded-full bg-sage/20 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Large faded watermark -->
  <div class="font-heading pointer-events-none absolute -right-6 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 select-none leading-none text-wm font-bold text-white/[0.04]"
    aria-hidden='true'>
    CÓMO
  </div>

  <div class='relative container-site'>
    <div class='grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 xl:gap-24 items-start'>

      <!-- ── LEFT: Headline block ─────────────────────────────────── -->
      <div class='lg:sticky lg:top-28'>
        <div data-animate class='mb-8'>
          <h2 class='text-sm italic font-bold text-cream'>
            Contratar un consultor SEO
          </h2>
        </div>

        <p
          data-animate
          class='font-heading text-h2 font-bold leading-tight text-cream tracking-tight'>
          <span class='text-white'>Pero se puede</span> solucionar<span class='text-teal'>.</span>
        </p>

        <div data-animate class='mt-6 flex items-center'>
          <div class='h-px w-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-cream/5 to-cream/35'></div>
          <div class='h-px w-10 bg-cream/60'></div>
        </div>

        <p
          data-animate
          class='mt-6 max-w-[40ch] text-p text-white leading-relaxed text-pretty'>
          En la llamada revisamos tu presencia en Google, analizamos a tu competencia y te digo exactamente <strong>qué está fallando</strong> y qué hay que hacer para que <strong>tus clientes te encuentren</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- ── RIGHT: 4-step process ────────────────────────────────── -->
      <div class='flex flex-col'>

        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div
          data-animate
          class='relative flex gap-6 py-10 border-b border-surface/10'>
          <div class='shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center pt-0.5 w-10'>
            <span class='text-[0.6rem] font-bold tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-teal leading-none mb-0.5'>
              Paso
            </span>
            <span
              class='font-heading text-[2.2rem] leading-none font-bold text-teal/40 tabular-nums'
>
              01
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class='text-base font-bold text-cream mb-3'>
              Agenda tu sesión gratuita
            </p>
            <CalButton variant="cream" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div
          data-animate
          class='relative flex gap-6 py-10 border-b border-surface/10'>
          <div class='shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center pt-0.5 w-10'>
            <span class='text-[0.6rem] font-bold tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-teal leading-none mb-0.5'>
              Paso
            </span>
            <span
              class='font-heading text-[2.2rem] leading-none font-bold text-teal/40 tabular-nums'
>
              02
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class='text-base font-bold text-cream mb-2'>
              Cuéntame tu situación
            </p>
            <p class='text-base text-white leading-relaxed'>
              Al reservar, indícame la URL de tu web y qué te preocupa. Nada más.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div
          data-animate
          class='relative flex gap-6 pt-10'>
          <div class='shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center pt-0.5 w-10'>
            <span class='text-[0.6rem] font-bold tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-teal leading-none mb-0.5'>
              Paso
            </span>
            <span
              class='font-heading text-[2.2rem] leading-none font-bold text-teal/40 tabular-nums'
>
              03
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class='text-base font-bold text-cream mb-2'>
              Hablamos 30 min
            </p>
            <p class='text-base text-white leading-relaxed text-pretty'>
              Reviso tu web en tiempo real, te explico qué está fallando y por qué Google no te muestra.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>


      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
